        <Parent_String>water features (landscaping) [300180674], landscaped-site elements [300139095], site elements [300078073], Open Spaces and Site Elements (hierarchy name ) [300139081], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
